  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libnvme</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libnvme</application> package is a library which provides
type definitions for NVMe specification structures, enumerations, and bit
fields, helper functions to construct, dispatch, and decode commands and
payloads, and utilities to connect, scan, and manage NVMe devices on a Linux
system.
    </para>

    &lfs120_checked;

